thread.title: CANADA STOCKS-TSX barely lower as healthcare, industrials slip
thread.title_full: CANADA STOCKS-TSX barely lower as healthcare, industrials slip | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: CANADA STOCKS-TSX barely lower as healthcare, industrials slip
text:
TORONTO Oct 20 Canada's main stock index was barely lower in early trade on Tuesday, with industrial and healthcare names slipping, offsetting financial and materials stocks.
The Toronto Stock Exchange's S&P/TSX composite index was down 10.53 points, or 0.08 percent, at 13,747.85 shortly after the open. (Reporting by Alastair Sharp ; Editing by Jeffrey Benkoe)
